'''羅德島設計學院'''（{{lang-en|'''Rhode Island School of Design'''}}，縮寫：'''{{lang|en|RISD}}''' {{IPAc-en|ˈ|r|ɪ|z|d|iː}}））是一所位于[[美国|美国]][[羅德島州|羅德島州]]首府[[普羅維登斯_(羅德島州)|普羅維登斯]]的[[私立大學|私立]]藝術學院。

該學院成立於1877年，位於普羅維登斯學院山（College Hill）山腳，校區與[[布朗大學|布朗大學]]相連。兩個學校共享師資與社群資源，並提供兩邊學生都可以參加的課程。[[RISD博物館|RISD博物館]]由該校維護。

==歷史==

[[File:RISD_Memorial_Hall.jpg|thumb]]
[[Image:Museum_of_Art,_RISD,_Providence_RI.jpg|thumb]]
1876年[[百年博覽會|百年博覽會]]上，一個叫做“Centennial Women”的組織募捐了一萬美元來組織女性作品展覽<ref>Austin, Nancy. Towards a Genealogy of Visual Culture at the Rhode Island School of Design, 1875–1900. Dissertation, Brown University. Ann Arbor: ProQuest/UMI, 2009. (Publication No. 3370099.)</ref><ref name="autogenerated1">Austin, Nancy. “What a Beginning is Worth”. Infinite Radius. Ed. Dawn Barrett and Andrew Martinez. (Providence: Rhode Island School of Design, 2008) 170–196.</ref>，會後還剩1,675美元<ref name="autogenerated1"/>，於是海倫·梅特卡夫（Helen Adelia Rowe Metcalf）提議用這些錢來辦一所教育機構。她的意見在1877年1月11日得到大多數人的讚同，於是在同年3月建校<ref>Austin, Nancy. “No Honors to Divide”. Infinite Radius. Ed. Dawn Barrett and Andrew Martinez. (Providence: Rhode Island School of Design, 2008) 197–217.</ref>，同年秋在普羅維登斯市中心開張<ref>Austin, Nancy. “A Place for Design: RISD at the Hoppin Homestead, 1878–1893.” Towards a Genealogy of Visual Culture at the Rhode Island School of Design, 1875–1900. Dissertation, Brown University. Ann Arbor: ProQuest/UMI, 2009. (Publication No. 3370099.)</ref>。梅特卡夫為第一任校長<ref>{{cite news | first=Laura Meade | last=Kirk | url=http://www.projo.com/yourlife/content/projo_20040321_womdraft.12a5f6.html | title=From bonnets to baccalaureates | work=[[The_Providence_Journal|The Providence Journal]] | date=2004-03-21 | accessdate=2007-10-17 | archive-date=2011-06-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629023017/http://www.projo.com/yourlife/content/projo_20040321_womdraft.12a5f6.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

